{"id":"6649","user":{"id":"194938","nickname":"提米","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/47/community/d2ViXzEwMDFfMTk0OTM4XzE5NDkzOF8xNjAzNTMwOTg5OTg0XzlkOTRkY2U3.png","subject_id":214,"work_shop_name":"疯癫工作室","work_shop_level":3,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"title":"【教程】画笔追随器","content":"<p>emmmm，这里是编程猫中级萌新，提米，给大家带来一个渣渣教程，大佬请跳过~</p>\n<p>成品：</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><iframe src=\"https://ide.codemao.cn/we/883422\" width=\"640\" height=\"498\"></iframe></p>\n<p>怎么制作出这样的效果捏~</p>\n<p>其实很简单啦~</p>\n<p>首先添加一个画笔的角色和一个追随器的角色~</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FmJDxGJE1hfO63SUksVe4DYkRxPq\"><br></p>\n<p>我们知道追随器的x轴和y轴是与画笔一样滴，所以新建两个链表，分别记录此时此刻画笔的x与y轴的值~、</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FtQN92Q_xO40OVyI-nRpygXGIUAt\"><br></p>\n<p>然后开启画笔功能，不停的输入x和Y的值，就像这样，接着按下回车，画笔停止画画，追随器开始运行。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FraG-zNB0JaX-ACtQ7f2all1vFHj\"><br></p>\n<p>当追随器开始运行时会不停地重复画笔x与y的值，我们为了方便追随器的重复执行的数字，和运行链表中的项数，我们加入一个变量“滑动次数”。</p>\n<p>拼接好积木后是这样的：<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FjMcScu1Xzu4wTFGpuqOFyUiHvPs\"></p>\n<p>运行你可能会发现追随器有时候运行太慢，所以我们可以在这里加入一个“等待0.05秒”的积木，让变量储存不那么频繁。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FpACIncIvNHP2Bdi6SLvo53--N2d\"><br></p>\n<p>然后就完成了，可以加一点别的积木是效果更好哟！</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<font color=\"#c0c0c0\">提米发布</font></p>\n<p><font color=\"#c0c0c